channel.title: Help with router
channel.description: Ok somehow my password and username for my router got changed so i did a factory reset and i can get on it now but now the wireless doesn't work my laptop just says acquiring network address and my ip is 0.0.0.0 is there a way i can fix this from my desktop because i can get on the internet on it or does anybody know?

item.description:

password: admin[/quote]after that see if your router is blocking your address (is your router a secured router with a password?).
Remember to always allow your IPv6 to access the router. idk if what i’m saying makes sence to you or not…
